Gaming | 2016 - 2018\n- Built multiplayer mobile games using React Native and Unity\n- Implemented in-app purchase system and user analytics tracking\nJunior iOS Developer | App Development Agency | 2015 - 2016\n- Developed iOS applications for various clients using Swift and Objective-C\n- Learned mobile development fundamentals and App Store submission process\nTechnical Skills\n- Mobile: 9 years iOS, 6 years Android, 5 years Swift, 4 years Kotlin, 3 years React Native\n- Backend: 5 years Python, 4 years Java, 6 years SQL\n- Leadership: 5 years Team Management, 4 years Architecture Design\n- Tools: 7 years Git, 3 years Docker\nEducation\nM.S. Software Engineering | University of Toronto | 2015\nB.S. Computer Science | Cairo University | 2013\n\", embedding:[-0.0076490627, -0.01527088, 0.011967411, -0.008255267, 0.006048413, 0.020583676, -0.03026931, -0.015338993, -0.0049892594, -0.017355131, 0.030923191, -0.0064741177, 0.01089123, -0.0029833387, -0.012682595, -0.0073766117, 0.018322332, 0.014072096, -0.019997906, -0.002763675, -0.026523108, -0.022858642, -0.013234309, -6.672922E-5, -0.0051867864, 0.0183632, 0.01446715, -0.026019074, 0.0022340985, -0.043837372, 0.032721367, -0.022736039, -0.024534214, 0.004927958, -0.025433304, 9.0334547E-4, 5.3026844E-5, 0.006440061, 0.025610397, 0.008779734, 0.019344022, 0.007941947, -0.0059564607, -0.0052344655, 0.006790842, 0.022272872, -0.028743584, -0.0119606005, -0.016633136, 0.029342975, -0.0018696951, 0.017627582, -0.0047985436, 0.01217175, -0.0048394115, -0.01713717, -0.022981245, 0.023035735, -0.009202033, 0.002303914, 0.007015614, 0.019725455, -0.0118856765, -0.00902494, -0.025610397, -0.0020348686, -0.004815572, 0.012410144, 0.012321598, 0.014494395, 0.04165776, 0.0034448027, -0.0133432895, 0.01591114, 0.020243112, -0.0053911246, -0.019180553, 0.010244159, -0.028961545, -0.017613959, -0.014235566, -0.031195642, 0.013200252, 0.027081633, 0.02141465, 0.042039193, -0.008820602, 0.0039709737, 0.0019684588, -0.016006498, 0.