croservices\n- Built infrastructure monitoring platform providing real-time visibility into system health\nSystems Administrator | Web Hosting | 2019 - 2020\n- Managed Linux server infrastructure supporting 10,000+ customer websites\n- Learned automation and infrastructure-as-code principles\nTechnical Skills\n- SRE: 5 years Site Reliability Engineering, 4 years Incident Response, 3 years Chaos Engineering\n- Programming: 5 years Python, 3 years Go, 4 years Linux\n- Infrastructure: 4 years Kubernetes, 5 years Docker, 3 years Terraform\n- Monitoring: 3 years Prometheus, 2 years Grafana\nEducation\nB.S. Computer Science | Technical University of Delft | 2019\n\", embedding:[0.0044095754, -0.037650205, 0.014200675, -0.010974489, 0.0043686517, 0.030911364, -0.018170316, -0.010312882, -0.02434986, -0.0053678825, 0.01821124, 0.01810211, 5.214097E-5, -0.0014084723, -7.433486E-5, -0.014405295, 0.03009288, -0.008205289, 0.004129927, -0.015905848, -0.018361295, -0.007570965, -0.005613427, -0.0069605135, -0.009623992, -0.0072299307, 0.017583737, -0.030802233, 0.00504731, -0.03975098, 0.009289779, -0.033230398, -0.0144735025, 0.0016531645, -0.019288909, -0.0024724999, 0.025291115, 0.007379986, 0.01602862, -0.018443143, 0.006817279, 0.025850412, 0.009664916, -0.035249323, -0.014173392, 0.019152496, -0.02286295, -0.017229062, -0.0034580894, 0.029710922, 0.021717075, -6.449814E-4, -0.009139723, 0.006165903, -0.0070798756, -0.017160853, -0.023558661, 0.025768563, -0.0033404324, -0.029328963, 3.724736E-5, -0.0054872446, -0.0066945064, -0.009392089, -0.019220702, -0.017761074, -0.024186164, 0.0061283894, 0.006609248, 0.009317062, 0.054756492, 0.024813667, -0.0014962887, 0.0012584171, 0.03792303, -0.011799793, -8.589805E-4, 0.0020035775, -0.0012575645, -0.014800896, -0.0024520378, -0.026477916, 0.008116621, 0.0040446687, 0.03363964, 0.023108495, 0.0010256611, -0.003819586, -0.010333344, -0.01604226, 0.0021041827, 0.039369017, 0.004225417, 0.020571198, -0.015032799, 0.017542813, -8.168